title: Guess Whos High Or Drunk 4/20 Special - Off The Rails #32
description: Today we play an upgraded version of Guess Who's High to celebrate the holiday of 4/20- Guess who's high, drunk, crossfaded or sober! The whole gang undergoes INTENSE questioning from Mr Ethan Klein as we try to determine which is which. We also discuss Jaden Smith's inspirational statements on the playground, Logan Paul's latest NFT scam, & much more!
